data.title: Journal of Finance and Accounting Research
data.meta_description: Journal-of-Finance-and-Accounting-research - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document is the journal of finance and accounting research from Vietnam. It contains summaries of several academic papers on topics related to finance, economics, and accounting in Vietnam. The papers explore issues such as tax policy, public investment, attracting foreign investment, digital transformation in agriculture, cultural development and the economy, accounting standards, and consumer behavior.
